divs: Sighting DetailsI just watched a small plane flew from The west.I was not expected to see about 30 white sphere clusters above to pass the plane. The time was 12'clock P.M. is about 5 minutes less. And also, I saw two objects came from The North to The south,I got a small binocular to see two cylinders's color is grey and light white, I did not know what it was. In few minutes, also I saw one sphere floated from The East to The West , Again I looked a binocular the color is orange floated and flashed was strange to me that the day was on October 20th was delighted to me,wow.
